Famous Nigerian music artiste, Peter Okoye of the P-Square group has called on Nigerians to retire failed politicians and take back the country. The Music singer also said it’s a shame politicians don’t have regard for Nigerians. He disclosed this in a post via his verified Twitter handle. Okoye advised Nigerians to ensure they collect their permanent voters card, PVC. He wrote, “Just look at the kind of people ruling our dear country Nigeria! These politicians and failed leaders don’t rate us at all! Shame. Pls go and collect your PVC, let’s retire them and take back our country! Enough is Enough! VOTE @PeterObi & @NgLabour.”